<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q48_v1" title="Q48_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una prueba, cinco estudiantes obtuvieron los siguientes puntajes: 65, <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, 72, 78 y 80. Se sabe que el promedio de estos puntajes fue <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
    <p>¿Cuál fue el puntaje de x?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">77<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>77</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>77</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>372</m:mn></m:math>. Pero con promedio <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math> y 5 estudiantes, la suma debe ser <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>372</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>, 77 no puede ser el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">70<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si el promedio de 5 puntajes es <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math>, la suma total es <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>. La suma de los puntajes conocidos es <m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>295</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>295</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">73,75<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>73,75</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>73,75</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>368,75</m:mn></m:math>. Pero la suma que corresponde a un promedio de <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math> en 5 estudiantes es <m:math><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>368,75</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>, 73,75 no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">69<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>69</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>69</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>364</m:mn></m:math>. Pero con promedio <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math> la suma debe ser <m:math><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>364</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>, 69 no puede ser el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Usar la definición de promedio</strong></p>
            <p>El promedio se calcula dividiendo la suma de los puntajes por la cantidad de estudiantes.</p>
            <p>Como hay 5 estudiantes y el promedio es <m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:math>, la suma total de los puntajes debe ser:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>73</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar los puntajes conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>Los puntajes conocidos son 65, 72, 78 y 80.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>137</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>137</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>215</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>215</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>295</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, la suma de los puntajes conocidos es <m:math><m:mn>295</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Encontrar el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>La suma total debe ser <m:math><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math>, así que restamos la suma conocida:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>295</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar</strong></p>
            <p>Reemplazamos <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> por <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>365</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Y el promedio es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>365</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>73</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El puntaje de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> fue <strong>70</strong>, es decir, la alternativa <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>